OMEMO Multi-End Message and Object EncryptionOMEMO 多端消息和对象加密

OMEMO is an XMPP Extension Protocol (XEP) for secure multi-client end-to-end encryption. It is an open standard based on a Double Ratchet and PEP which can be freely used and implemented by anyone. The protocol has been audited by a third party.OMEMO 是一种 XMPP 扩展协议 (XEP)，用于安全的多客户端端到端加密。它是一个基于 Double Ratchet 和 PEP 的开放标准，任何人都可以自由使用和实施。该协议已经过第三方审核。

Benefits好处

The OMEMO encryption /oˈmiːmoʊ/ (OMEMO Multi-End Message and Object Encryption) gives you all the advantages you would expect from a modern-day encryption protocol like Future and Forward Secrecy and deniability while allowing you to keep the benefits of message synchronization and offline delivery.OMEMO 加密 /oˈmiːmoʊ/（OMEMO 多端消息和对象加密）为您提供现代加密协议所期望的所有优势，例如未来和前向保密性和可否认性，同时让您保持消息同步和离线的优势送货。

OMEMO not only gives you a better encryption features than OpenPGP and OTR but is also much easier to setup. OMEMO is the encryption you can actually use in your daily life. Turn it on once and forget you ever did.OMEMO 不仅为您提供比 OpenPGP 和 OTR 更好的加密功能，而且更易于设置。 OMEMO 是您可以在日常生活中实际使用的加密。打开它一次，忘记你曾经做过。

OMEMO is available right now in the Android XMPP-Client Conversations (Buy on Google Play), the iOS client ChatSecure, or as a plugin for the Desktop client Gajim.OMEMO 现在可以在 Android XMPP-Client Conversations（在 Google Play 上购买）、iOS 客户端 ChatSecure 或桌面客户端 Gajim 的插件中使用。

Device Trust设备信任

With OMEMO you no longer trust user identities but device identities. If you are communicating with a contact for the first time or if that contact recently got a new device, you will be presented with a fingerprint for that device. You can then either verify that fingerprint out of band (for example via a quick phone call) or, if you are reasonably sure that your transport is secure (for instance if you are chatting on the same, trusted server), you can choose to trust a device on first use. If you have trusted devices of your contact in the past you can also use those devices as a secure channel to verify the fingerprint of a new device by having your contact verify the fingerprint via chat.使用 OMEMO，您不再信任用户身份，而是设备身份。如果您是第一次与联系人通信，或者如果该联系人最近获得了新设备，您将看到该设备的指纹。然后，您可以在带外验证指纹（例如通过快速电话），或者，如果您有理由确定您的传输是安全的（例如，如果您在同一台受信任的服务器上聊天），您可以选择信任第一次使用的设备。如果您过去信任联系人的设备，您还可以将这些设备用作安全通道，通过让您的联系人通过聊天验证指纹来验证新设备的指纹。

Background背景

OMEMO uses a Double Ratchet to establish secure sessions between every combination of devices for you and your contact. Those sessions are then being used to communicate secure keys to all devices. OMEMO will generate a new key for every message. That key is used to encrypt your message with AES-GCM. The long-lived Double Ratchet sessions in the background deal with the challenges of message reordering, message loss and accidental duplication.OMEMO 使用双棘轮在您和您的联系人的每种设备组合之间建立安全会话。然后使用这些会话将安全密钥传递给所有设备。 OMEMO 将为每条消息生成一个新密钥。该密钥用于使用 AES-GCM 加密您的消息。后台的长期双棘轮会议处理消息重新排序、消息丢失和意外重复的挑战。

Being built upon PEP (Personal Eventing Protocol) to announce the pre-keys used by the Double Ratchet to establish new sessions, OMEMO requires little to no change to the existing XMPP server infrastructure.OMEMO 基于 PEP（个人事件协议）来宣布双棘轮协议用于建立新会话的预密钥，几乎不需要对现有 XMPP 服务器基础设施进行任何更改。

Find more information in XEP-0384: OMEMO Encryption.在 XEP-0384 中找到更多信息：OMEMO 加密。

Finally I can send encrypted messages to someone who is currently offline, uses mulitple clients and simultaneously receive a copy of that message on all of my devices.最后，我可以将加密消息发送给当前处于离线状态、使用多个客户端并同时在我的所有设备上接收该消息的副本的人。

A pleasantly surprised user惊喜的用户
